---
title: Bacon Gnocchi Carbonara with Spinach & Pear Salad
description: Pillowy potato gnocchi pairs perfectly with cheesy bacon carbonara. Try saying that 10 times, fast! This tongue twister is also a tastebud pleaser, especially with the crisp spinach and pear salad served on the side.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d9404c8b35cc67062453171-4fd82b1f.jpg
